General.Name: Happy Valley Nutrition Ltd
General.Description: Happy Valley Nutrition Limited engages in the production and sale of infant milk formula and other nutritional products in New Zealand and internationally. The company was formerly known as Happy Valley Milk Limited and changed its name to Happy Valley Nutrition Limited in September 2019. Happy Valley Nutrition Limited was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Auckland, New Zealand.
